  "title": "\"Redemption Song\" | John Legend",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12985.0,
      "end_time": 15767.0,
      "text": "At Free America, we&#39;ve done a listening and learning tour."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16390.0,
      "end_time": 19834.0,
      "text": "We visited not only with prosecutors"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19858.0,
      "end_time": 21604.0,
      "text": "but with legislators,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21628.0,
      "end_time": 26489.0,
      "text": "with inmates in our state and local prisons."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27282.0,
      "end_time": 29932.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve gone to immigration detention centers."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30239.0,
      "end_time": 31675.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve met a lot of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33174.0,
      "end_time": 39397.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve seen that redemption and transformation can happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39422.0,
      "end_time": 44108.0,
      "text": "in our prisons, our jails and our immigration detention centers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 44133.0,
      "end_time": 47150.0,
      "text": "giving hope to those who want to create a better life"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 47174.0,
      "end_time": 48842.0,
      "text": "after serving their time."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 50280.0,
      "end_time": 53596.0,
      "text": "Imagine if we also considered the front end of this prison pipeline."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 53964.0,
      "end_time": 55905.0,
      "text": "What would it look like if we intervened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55929.0,
      "end_time": 58882.0,
      "text": "with rehabilitation as a core value --"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58906.0,
      "end_time": 61940.0,
      "text": "with love and compassion as core values?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 62523.0,
      "end_time": 64822.0,
      "text": "We would have a society that is safer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 64846.0,
      "end_time": 65997.0,
      "text": "healthier"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 66210.0,
      "end_time": 67870.0,
      "text": "and worthy of raising our children in."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68864.0,
      "end_time": 71536.0,
      "text": "I want to introduce you to James Cavitt."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72360.0,
      "end_time": 76539.0,
      "text": "James served 12 years in the San Quentin State Prison"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 76563.0,
      "end_time": 79213.0,
      "text": "and is being released in 18 months."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 79809.0,
      "end_time": 81774.0,
      "text": "Now James, like you and me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81798.0,
      "end_time": 84714.0,
      "text": "is more than the worst thing he&#39;s done."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 85691.0,
      "end_time": 88608.0,
      "text": "He is a father, a husband, a son, a poet."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 89265.0,
      "end_time": 90882.0,
      "text": "He committed a crime;"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90906.0,
      "end_time": 92523.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s paying his debt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 92547.0,
      "end_time": 95110.0,
      "text": "and working hard to build the skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95350.0,
      "end_time": 98122.0,
      "text": "to make the transition back to a productive life"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 98762.0,
      "end_time": 101783.0,
      "text": "when he enters the civilian population again."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 101807.0,
      "end_time": 104461.0,
      "text": "Now James, like millions of people behind bars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 104485.0,
      "end_time": 106520.0,
      "text": "is an example of what happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 106544.0,
      "end_time": 110994.0,
      "text": "if we believe that our failings don&#39;t define who we are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 111190.0,
      "end_time": 113321.0,
      "text": "that we are all worthy of redemption"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 113345.0,
      "end_time": 117582.0,
      "text": "and if we support those impacted by mass incarceration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 117606.0,
      "end_time": 119232.0,
      "text": "we can all heal together."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 120340.0,
      "end_time": 122320.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to introduce you to James right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 122344.0,
      "end_time": 124827.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s going to share his journey of redemption"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124852.0,
      "end_time": 126200.0,
      "text": "through spoken word."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128431.00000000001,
      "end_time": 129781.00000000001,
      "text": "James Cavitt: Thanks, John."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 129806.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131721.0,
      "text": "TED, welcome to San Quentin."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 132521.0,
      "end_time": 135195.0,
      "text": "The talent is abundant behind prison walls."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135608.0,
      "end_time": 137640.0,
      "text": "Future software engineers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137664.0,
      "end_time": 138942.0,
      "text": "entrepreneurs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 138967.0,
      "end_time": 140118.0,
      "text": "craftsmen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 140142.0,
      "end_time": 141293.0,
      "text": "musicians"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141317.0,
      "end_time": 142600.0,
      "text": "and artists."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 142624.0,
      "end_time": 145721.0,
      "text": "This piece is inspired by all of the hard work"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 145745.0,
      "end_time": 148973.0,
      "text": "that men and women are doing on the inside"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 148997.0,
      "end_time": 152322.0,
      "text": "to create better lives and futures for themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 152346.0,
      "end_time": 154179.0,
      "text": "after they serve their time."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 154931.0,
      "end_time": 158518.0,
      "text": "This piece is entitled, \"Where I Live.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 160218.0,
      "end_time": 163851.0,
      "text": "I live in a world where most people are too afraid to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 164441.0,
      "end_time": 166777.0,
      "text": "Surrounded by tall, concrete walls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 166801.0,
      "end_time": 167952.0,
      "text": "steel bars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 167976.0,
      "end_time": 169270.0,
      "text": "where razor wire have a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 169294.0,
      "end_time": 172380.0,
      "text": "of cutting away at the hopes for a brighter tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 173697.0,
      "end_time": 174848.0,
      "text": "I live in a world"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 174872.0,
      "end_time": 176405.0,
      "text": "that kill people who kill people"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 176429.0,
      "end_time": 177580.0,
      "text": "in order to teach people"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 177604.0,
      "end_time": 179000.0,
      "text": "that killing people is wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 180285.0,
      "end_time": 181577.0,
      "text": "Imagine that."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 182111.0,
      "end_time": 183262.0,
      "text": "Better yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 183286.0,
      "end_time": 186356.0,
      "text": "imagine a world where healed people helped hurt people heal"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 186380.0,
      "end_time": 187632.0,
      "text": "and become strong."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 188427.0,
      "end_time": 191618.0,
      "text": "Maybe then we would all be singin&#39; \"Redemption Song.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 193800.0,
      "end_time": 195989.0,
      "text": "I live in a world that has been called \"hell on Earth\""
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 196130.0,
      "end_time": 197723.0,
      "text": "by those trapped inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 199460.0,
      "end_time": 200969.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;ve come to the stark realization"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 200993.0,
      "end_time": 202197.0,
      "text": "that prison --"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 202780.0,
      "end_time": 204316.0,
      "text": "it really is what you make it."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 205192.0,
      "end_time": 207907.0,
      "text": "You see, in spite of the harshness of my reality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 207931.0,
      "end_time": 209391.0,
      "text": "there is a silver lining."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 210470.0,
      "end_time": 212288.0,
      "text": "I knew that my freedom was gonna come,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 212312.0,
      "end_time": 213701.0,
      "text": "it was just a matter of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 213725.0,
      "end_time": 217117.0,
      "text": "And so I treated my first steps as if they were my last mile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 217141.0,
      "end_time": 220970.0,
      "text": "and I realized that you don&#39;t have to be free"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 220122.0,
      "end_time": 221791.0,
      "text": "in order to experience freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 222890.0,
      "end_time": 224648.0,
      "text": "And just because you&#39;re free,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 224673.0,
      "end_time": 226470.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t mean that you have freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 226996.0,
      "end_time": 230242.0,
      "text": "Many of us, for years, have been battling our inner demons."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 230266.0,
      "end_time": 233607.0,
      "text": "We walk around smiling when inside we&#39;re really screamin&#39;:"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 233631.0,
      "end_time": 234781.0,
      "text": "freedom!"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 236171.0,
      "end_time": 237321.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t you get it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 238180.0,
      "end_time": 239503.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re all serving time;"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 239527.0,
      "end_time": 241990.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re just in different places."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 241780.0,
      "end_time": 242931.0,
      "text": "As for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 242955.0,
      "end_time": 245535.0,
      "text": "I choose to be free from the prisons I&#39;ve created."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 245559.0,
      "end_time": 246710.0,
      "text": "The key:"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 246734.0,
      "end_time": 247885.0,
      "text": "forgiveness."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 247909.0,
      "end_time": 249600.0,
      "text": "Action&#39;s my witness."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 249840.0,
      "end_time": 250234.0,
      "text": "If we want freedom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 251122.0,
      "end_time": 252669.0,
      "text": "then we gotta think different."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 253690.0,
      "end_time": 254840.0,
      "text": "Because freedom ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 257226.0,
      "end_time": 258376.0,
      "text": "it isn&#39;t a place."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 259783.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260933.00000000003,
      "text": "It&#39;s a mind setting."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 262996.0,
      "end_time": 264147.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
