      "text": "(Piano)"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 285789.0,
      "end_time": 288710.0,
      "text": "John Legend: Old pirates, yes, they rob I."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 290233.0,
      "end_time": 292987.0,
      "text": "Sold I to the merchant ships."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 295414.0,
