      "text": "triumphantly."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 321343.0,
      "end_time": 324851.0,
      "text": "Won&#39;t you help to sing"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 326686.0,
      "end_time": 329400.0,
      "text": "these songs of freedom?"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 329899.0,
      "end_time": 332754.0,
      "text": "&#39;Cause all I ever had --"
    },
    {
